data.title: Episode 2720 (29 April 2004)
data.meta_description: Den is paid a visit by a mystery woman, while Laura seizes the chance to humiliate Janine at Angie's Den. Meanwhile, Zoe dresses to impress and Dennis is her target. Den Watts - Leslie Grantham Chrissie Watts - Tracy-Ann Oberman Sharon Watts - Letitia Dean Dennis Rickman - Nigel Harman Vicki...
data.text:
When Janine flaunts her date - a handsome businessman - at Angie's Den's opening night, Laura takes the opportunity to tell him about Janine's sordid past. On the receiving end for once, Janine leaves the club in tears but vows revenge. She follows Laura home and confronts her.

Den receives a shock when a mystery woman arrives at the club - he steers her away from his family.

Spencer is upset to have a spot on his chin when he is trying hard to impress Zoe.

Vicki and Sharon put up posters about the club opening.

Garry discovers that Minty is a mechanic. He admits that he can't ride Mark's bike. Garry babysits while Laura and Pat go to the club opening.

Dennis chucks some under-age girls out. The boys all appreciate Zoe's sexy dress.

Janine and Michael agree to sign the contract but Laura tells him that Janine used to be a prostitute. He asks Janine how much she charges before ripping the contract up. Janine goes to Pat's flat and she and Laura fight.

Billy shows Chrissie into the club to find Den.

Pat finds Laura sobbing.

Chrissie reveals that she is Den's wife.
